🔬 STEP 4: AUTHORIZATION ANALYSIS MODEL

4.1 IDENTIFY SUBJECTS

- Authenticated users
- Roles (admin, user, guest)
- Service accounts

---

4.2 IDENTIFY OBJECTS

- Resources (records, files, APIs)
- Sensitive operations
- Data entities

---

4.3 IDENTIFY ACTIONS

- Read / Write / Update / Delete
- Administrative actions
- Privileged operations

---

4.4 TRACE ACCESS FLOW (MANDATORY)

For EACH protected resource:

- Trace:
  user → role/identity → access check → resource access

---

🧨 STEP 5: FULL AUTHORIZATION VULNERABILITY COVERAGE

You MUST check ALL:

---

5.1 Missing Authorization (CWE-862)

- No access control check before resource access

---

5.2 Broken Object Level Authorization (IDOR)

- Direct object reference without validation
- User accessing other users' data

---

5.3 Broken Function Level Authorization

- Access to restricted endpoints without proper role checks

---

5.4 Privilege Escalation (CWE-269)

- Horizontal escalation (user → another user)
- Vertical escalation (user → admin)

---

5.5 Insecure Direct Object References

- IDs passed directly without ownership validation

---

5.6 Role Misconfiguration

- Incorrect role mapping
- Over-permissive roles

---

5.7 Forced Browsing

- Accessing hidden/restricted endpoints directly

---

5.8 Missing Ownership Validation

- No check if resource belongs to user

---

5.9 Policy Enforcement Gaps

- Checks implemented inconsistently
- Some endpoints protected, others not

---

5.10 Client-Side Access Control

- Authorization enforced only on frontend

---

🛡️ STEP 6: MITIGATION VALIDATION

SAFE CONTROLS:

- Server-side authorization checks
- RBAC/ABAC enforcement
- Ownership validation
- Centralized middleware enforcement

---

UNSAFE CONTROLS:

- Client-side checks only
- Hardcoded role checks without validation
- Partial enforcement

---

DECISION:

- Proper enforcement → Protected
- Missing/bypassable → Vulnerable
- Cannot verify → Not Confirmed

---

🔄 STEP 7: CROSS-FILE ANALYSIS

- Track access checks across:
  
  - Controllers
  - Middleware
  - Services

- Verify consistency across all entry points

